\Phi_{I\alpha}\left(r\text{,\ensuremath{\varphi},\ensuremath{\theta}}\right)=\sum_{l=m}^{L}\left\{ A^{l}\left(m,n,p\right)u_{l}\left(E_{lq},r\right)+B^{l}\left(m,n,p\right)g_{l}\left(E_{lq},r\right)\right\} Y_{lm}\left(\varphi,\theta\right)
